00:02:02.070 --> 00:02:05.230
(Dragon King's Decree)

00:02:05.650 --> 00:02:06.890
This is incredibly precious.

00:02:07.570 --> 00:02:08.530
Why give it to me?

00:02:11.650 --> 00:02:13.530
My mother stole Miss Yue's identity.

00:02:14.210 --> 00:02:16.280
Everything we had was never ours
to begin with.

00:02:17.730 --> 00:02:19.450
You're her daughter.

00:02:19.850 --> 00:02:21.280
You have every right to see it.

00:02:21.770 --> 00:02:23.450
This isn't the real decree.

00:02:24.210 --> 00:02:26.330
It's only a record about it.

00:02:27.130 --> 00:02:28.690
It describes the old days,

00:02:29.370 --> 00:02:30.810
when Wujing's ancestors fought dragons

00:02:30.810 --> 00:02:31.850
and even married them.

00:02:33.090 --> 00:02:35.610
As for why dragons married women
of the Wujing Saintess' bloodline,

00:02:36.010 --> 00:02:37.210
and the decree's secrets...

00:02:37.930 --> 00:02:39.650
Maybe the answers are in here.

00:02:49.010 --> 00:02:50.370
(Storm and thunder, )

00:02:50.370 --> 00:02:51.610
(master of all.)

00:02:51.770 --> 00:02:53.250
(Swimming like a fish, )

00:02:53.330 --> 00:02:54.970
(flying like a bird.)

00:02:54.970 --> 00:02:57.050
(Walking the earth the way we do.)

00:02:57.490 --> 00:02:59.090
(Dragons rule all beasts.)

00:02:59.090 --> 00:03:00.290
(The pinnacle of all creatures.)

00:03:00.290 --> 00:03:01.570
(A god among them.)

00:03:02.410 --> 00:03:04.290
(The Dragon King leads the sanctuary.)

00:03:04.290 --> 00:03:05.370
(Wujing of the mortal realm)

00:03:05.370 --> 00:03:08.770
(and beasts of other realms bow to him.)

00:03:09.210 --> 00:03:10.090
(The Wujing Saintess)

00:03:10.450 --> 00:03:11.370
(is born blessed)

00:03:11.730 --> 00:03:12.930
(and sees what others miss.)

00:03:13.650 --> 00:03:16.010
(When demons invade the mortal realm, )

00:03:16.010 --> 00:03:18.130
(she dons a battle robe and gold armor.)

00:03:18.130 --> 00:03:20.050
(With a crown and jade belt, )

00:03:20.050 --> 00:03:21.770
(and the Icebound Sword in hand, )

00:03:21.930 --> 00:03:22.930
(she rides dragons)

00:03:23.010 --> 00:03:24.130
(and fights demons.)

00:03:24.410 --> 00:03:25.690
(She is fearless.)

00:03:25.890 --> 00:03:28.570
(She forged a blood pact with dragons.)

00:03:28.570 --> 00:03:31.170
(That's why her bloodline is so strong.)

00:03:31.490 --> 00:03:34.730
(If a dragon marries a woman
of the Wujing Saintess' bloodline, )

00:03:34.850 --> 00:03:37.050
(their child is half-dragon.)

00:03:37.050 --> 00:03:38.530
(They're born powerful)

00:03:38.690 --> 00:03:40.890
(and are fiercely protective.)

00:03:41.250 --> 00:03:43.050
(A clear sign of pregnancy)

00:03:43.290 --> 00:03:45.050
(is a red dragon mark)

00:03:45.050 --> 00:03:48.290
(right below the belly button.)

00:03:50.530 --> 00:03:51.330
Miss,

00:03:51.610 --> 00:03:52.730
it says here

00:03:52.850 --> 00:03:55.690
that dragon eggs
take three years and six months.

00:03:56.250 --> 00:03:57.530
So when it's born,

00:03:58.530 --> 00:04:00.370
will it be a dragon or a human?

00:04:01.050 --> 00:04:01.850
No clue.

00:04:01.850 --> 00:04:03.210
It doesn't say.

00:04:06.970 --> 00:04:09.690
Young Master still
doesn't know about the child.

00:04:11.450 --> 00:04:12.010
Hunbao,

00:04:12.610 --> 00:04:14.290
you can't tell anyone.

00:04:15.050 --> 00:04:15.890
Why not?

00:04:15.970 --> 00:04:16.610
Miss,

00:04:16.730 --> 00:04:17.730
think about it.

00:04:17.730 --> 00:04:19.570
You are the real Wujing Saintess.

00:04:19.570 --> 00:04:21.250
Liluo stole everything from you!

00:04:21.570 --> 00:04:23.650
And now you're carrying a dragon child.

00:04:23.770 --> 00:04:25.530
Everyone will believe you now.

00:04:25.890 --> 00:04:27.890
You can take back what's yours!

00:04:31.890 --> 00:04:34.370
You're always with Fei Yuan.
You pick up nothing good from him.

00:04:34.570 --> 00:04:35.690
But you sure copied

00:04:35.690 --> 00:04:36.890
his boldness.

00:04:36.970 --> 00:04:37.930
No, I didn't!

00:04:38.290 --> 00:04:39.610
It's just that Liluo's mess

00:04:39.890 --> 00:04:41.970
means you and Young Master
can't be together.

00:04:42.330 --> 00:04:45.170
You've been spacing out a lot lately.

00:04:45.490 --> 00:04:47.050
Even I'm getting worried.

00:04:47.090 --> 00:04:47.970
You little fool.

00:04:49.170 --> 00:04:50.890
I live on the edge every single day.

00:04:51.370 --> 00:04:52.650
I can't let this get out.

00:04:53.210 --> 00:04:54.050
If the baby

00:04:54.770 --> 00:04:56.090
becomes my weakness,

00:04:57.010 --> 00:04:58.330
they'd tear me apart.

00:04:58.890 --> 00:05:01.010
I didn't think it through.

00:05:01.930 --> 00:05:03.810
Honestly, the moment I saw my mother,

00:05:04.690 --> 00:05:06.650
I knew I was the Wujing Saintess.

00:05:07.130 --> 00:05:08.530
But people always say

00:05:08.850 --> 00:05:10.770
that the Wujing Saintess
marrying a dragon

00:05:11.490 --> 00:05:12.890
will repair the broken barrier

00:05:13.050 --> 00:05:14.210
around the sanctuary.

00:05:14.570 --> 00:05:15.530
So why is it

00:05:15.850 --> 00:05:16.970
that Chu Moshang and I

00:05:17.170 --> 00:05:18.970
are basically already married
in our hearts,

00:05:19.650 --> 00:05:20.890
yet the barrier

00:05:20.970 --> 00:05:22.170
is still falling apart?

00:05:23.930 --> 00:05:26.770
Maybe this book got it wrong?

00:05:27.890 --> 00:05:28.730
Maybe

00:05:29.810 --> 00:05:31.250
there's another meaning behind it.

00:05:35.490 --> 00:05:36.810
We need to find the Young Lord

00:05:36.970 --> 00:05:37.930
and talk this through.

00:05:38.170 --> 00:05:39.810
Now that Mother and I have reunited,

00:05:40.250 --> 00:05:41.250
we need to get her

00:05:41.610 --> 00:05:42.490
out of Wujing City fast

00:05:43.050 --> 00:05:44.450
before Liluo and Li Yue notice.

00:05:45.010 --> 00:05:45.530
Alright.

00:06:06.330 --> 00:06:07.490
Feng Zhilou,

00:06:08.210 --> 00:06:10.010
you were really hard to track down.

00:06:10.530 --> 00:06:11.530
What do you want?

00:06:12.130 --> 00:06:13.210
Miss Zhilou,

00:06:14.370 --> 00:06:16.370
you're so invested in dragon affairs.

00:06:16.690 --> 00:06:18.330
Why not ask me directly?

00:06:19.370 --> 00:06:20.970
What good is that dusty book?

00:06:22.010 --> 00:06:23.130
No book can beat

00:06:23.330 --> 00:06:24.970
an actual dragon's answer,

00:06:25.290 --> 00:06:26.890
right?

00:06:29.530 --> 00:06:30.530
Anyway,

00:06:31.250 --> 00:06:32.770
